She looked at Paralysis. She shrugged her shoulders. "Well, let's get 
to it." 
She went tot he main comtrol panel andreenterd the codes of the 
computer to accept herself, Paralysis, and Quickstrike for 
authorizing commands.  She looked at the monitor for a moment.  She 
aimed two of the mamual guns at the Maximals and aimed at thier feet. 
or inches above thier heads.  She looked at Paralysis. "Opps, my aim 
is a little off." She said with a slight blush in her face.  She face 
the monitor and fored again, still hitting ground inches from the 
maximal that she was aiming at.
